t using the PetInfo window button.  The problem is that there is a small couple tenths of a second delay sometimes on the button press.  If you back off a bit and hit the button with a little more time left on the spell timer, it will work 100% of the time.  Just hit the button a little earlier on the timer than you do with using /pet get lost  from chat.<br>
